content.title: Coat Rack, Freestanding Coat Rack with 8 Hooks and 3 Adjustable Size Tree Coat Racks for Bedroom, Hallway, Entrance, Office, for Hats, Coats, Scarves, Handbags
content.bullet_points:
【PREMIUM WOODEN MATERIAL】- Wangmuxia wooden coat rack is made of high-quality New Zealand pinewood screw-on pieces and 3 prong legs for optimal stability that supports multiple garments and outerwear.
【ADJUSTABLE HEIGHT for USAGE】- 4 sections design and you can customize the rack height and hooks as you like. 2-section heigth (39.5”) can be put at beside, 3 sections height (54.2”) is for for a kid use, 4-section height (68.8”) is for adult use.
【EASY TO ASSEMBLE】- No Tools Required. The coat rack is equipped with metal screw holes. You can assemble it with our assembly instruction manual in just a few minutes.
【ECONOMICAL and PRACTICAL】- It is so practical with cheap price. Its 8 sturdy hooks allow you to hang hats, scarves, backpacks, ties, and umbrellas or any other things you want.
【SPACE SAVING】- The free standing coat rack takes up little space in entryway, living rooms, bedroom, office and any other places. With it you can make your room much more neat and clean.
